Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[crash]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps, crash]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] How am I\Nsupposed to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,when there's not even a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Or at least there's\Nno door that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO crying]\NYuki! Wake up! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki... Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Please say something, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I'm supposed to\Nbelieve there isn't a door,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I just have to select it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] We'll be in trouble\Nif that groundskeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,finds us in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO crying]\NPlease... Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhat a sight to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Those tears of yours, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,They shine like gems.\NThey're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I wanted to be\Nyour LRIG so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the strongest\NSelector I'd ever encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,With you, I knew that\NI could defeat anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and I longed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help my desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I was formed from Mayu's sorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,darkness, filth,\Nand pain, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,All those horrible feelings,\Nthey echoed in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But, as I battled\Nalongside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Your warmth and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It did more than just touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It illuminated me\Nand began to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NAnd as it did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt something beautiful\Nand precious overcome me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,My heart, however corrupt,\Nhad been born anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And best of all,\Nyou showed me something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That which I truly desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhile I can say it, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have\Nto thank me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,And stop making this sound\Nlike you're saying goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I don't understand.\NWhy is she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Parting wasn't\Nthis painful for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it that\Nthe two of them have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH]\NAww...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Boo-hoo, you're gonna lose\Nyour special widdle buddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,as if I gave a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The Battle ends when a LRIG\Ndisappears, so you lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,unless she's still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So tell us, Iona,\Nor should I say, "Yuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you still battle,\Nor have you vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru and Yuki\Nwon't lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,--[MAYU] Shiro!\N--[RUKO] Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Impossible!\NHow did she get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You can win. Just use Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Make me and Yuki into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NTama, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you\Nto do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't let me\Nbecome a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I would only corrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not corrupt.\NYou're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkling like snow\Nin the warm sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You think so? Really? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama is like the sun\Nthat shines in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're like the snow\Nthat falls in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So if you guys\Ncome together as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...you'll be like snow\Nfalling in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Level 5! Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you call out my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NBecause Tama is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,And the one who created\Nthem both is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But right now,\Nyou're not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't like you\Nvery much at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,because you made every one of us\Nwho played the game suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,These people are\Nin pain because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So many girls, scarred for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just their bodies,\Nbut their souls too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But there is a\Npart of you I do like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The true you that's\Nnext to me, Tama and Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if this\Nwasn't how things were,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,if we'd somehow met before you\Nstarted the Selector Battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have really liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And we would have been friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NStop it. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Is hearing something like that\Nsupposed to make me feel happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,We would have been friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You just want to bury me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Urith!\NAttack with Black Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Now you're\Ntalking, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NRu! Let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it sounds odd,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,but even if Selector Battles\Nthemselves are wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,They're still our only chance at\Nwinning the other Mayu over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,so we have to do this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[pounding noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh man, what a\Nsad-looking room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NMayu! Summon Arc Energe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NAttack with Laevateinn, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NStop it! That's my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAN'S VOICE]\NHow's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN'S VOICE] Well, she\Nhas a lack of appetite, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAN'S VOICE]\NYes, that was expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Increase the dosage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl. Her status?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,She's alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Ruko said her name\Nwith such concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,My name was never\Nspoken that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Dammit, would you\Nlook at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten\Nyou're the one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,who started the\NSelector Battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NSelector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Me? I didn't get\Nto select anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] It's not that\NI didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that I didn't have\Nany "selections" to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,While it looks like\NI took dreams and wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,away from everyone, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I gave all of them the\Nopportunity to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, I know that ended up\Nhurting some of them in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,but at least they had freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I was denied even that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] The only thing\Nthat connects this place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,to the outside\Nis that window, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,This tiny room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It was Mayu's entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I never had a chance to select.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Now tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd you seal\NTama away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why let Yuki be the\Nonly one who could battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\N"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Because she hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The world outside the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,a world that was\Nfilled with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)] In reality,\Nshe longed for that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She wanted to be a part\Nof it more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why just when\Nher life came to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu did indeed\Nmake a selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.44,Main,,0,0,0,,And with it, Tama awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Beyond the wall of black,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,beyond the wall of white,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,there existed a world\Nfull of countless shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, longing for\Nlight like Mayu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,was released into\Nthis colorful new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NYou're wrong! That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NLies... All lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.\NThat isn't like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Why don't you come\Nsee the outside world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,with all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We'd love to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NHow can you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I've long since died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh oh. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--[screaming]\N--[RUKO] Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to\Nprotect the LRIGs I created?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Back then, no one\Never tried to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No one held me\Nin their arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sure if this\Nwasn't how things were,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,if we'd somehow met before you\Nstarted the Selector Battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have really liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,And we would have been friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] If we had,\Ncould things have changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I thought if\NI were to die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,all alone and forgotten\Nby the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted others to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...that in some\Nsmall way I existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,and I wanted them to feel the\Npain of the life I lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if the only way\Nwas through hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] But...\NYou can change all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You can make friends! Real ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,And not through hatred\Nand hurting people, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what color\Ncard I selected, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Why do you\Nwant me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWith Urith at Level 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,she's able to control\Nall of the colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But you see, this move\Ncan only be used once, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can guess which color\NI selected, you win, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it wrong, and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] This card is\Nthe color of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat is she trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it the color of black?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The hatred she embodied by Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Or is it the color of white?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The love embodied by Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NBeyond the wall of black,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,beyond the wall of white,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,there existed a world\Nfull of countless shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH]\NHurry it up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna\Nmake me hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NSo tell me, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What color is this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the same\Nas this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So the "color" is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,There is none.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH]\NW-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu, please, you can't let me\Nbe executed without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I have nothing in\Nmy hand, and no Arts to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Simply put, I can't do\Nanything in this turn at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know why\NI chose non-colored?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Because it's one that erases all\Nand marks the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But that also means that\Nit marks a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And because of that, you can\Ncolor it any way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NPaint the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So you mean...\NI can have a second chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Then someone--Someone\Nwill hold me and call my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NRuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NWe need to act quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take our oath before\Nthis world disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But this time, let's make\Nyour real wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang on. But my wish--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It was to turn the\Ngirls who became LRIGs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,back to their original selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's to turn the girls\Nwho became LRIGs into humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Once you've returned\Nto your original form,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,then the Tama and Yuki\Nparts of you--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,They might\Nactually become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NRu, you're like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,making a selection means\None thing, not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I've made my selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going\Nto budge ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't make one choice\Nat the sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,of something\Nor someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how I'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if isn't easy and even\Nif it brings me pain and tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,that's still better than giving\Nup halfway or compromising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the selection\NI've made, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU (MERGED)]\NAs I said, just like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?\NYou're one to talk, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, MAYU (MERGED)] "I accept\Nthe laws of the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"And upon this sacred oath, a\Nnew Eternal Girl shall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Look, dear, that\Nbuilding's finally finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess the city didn't\Ndisappear after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my.\NWhy are you so dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have plans\Nwith your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,We're studying\Nfor the big exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NWhat about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'll be back by then,\Nbut in the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I've gotta run, Grandma. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--[RUKO] What the--?\N--[AYUMU] Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd think you'd be used to me\Nsleeping under here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, there is a couch in here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,you could sleep on\Ninstead, weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NBe careful, out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI will! See ya, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You have a great day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know any better, I'd\Nhardly recognize her anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU]\NGuess so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] That girl.\NShe's grown up so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NAww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,My brain can't take\Nany more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Um, but we've only\Nbeen at it for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NShe's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to go the\Nsame school as Hitoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,you've gotta really\Nbuckle down like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Just gimme some of your\Nbig brain? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hey. How about\Nwe take a break at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A break, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, YUZUKI, HITOE]\NLet's play WIXOSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NTrash Rhino with Tawil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wow, the Activation\NAbility on Yuzuki's new LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,is crazy powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki recommended\NI try some different cards
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,so I could learn\Na few new tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,And while I've gotten\Nbetter overall, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,none of the new LRIGs match me\Nnearly as well as Hanayo did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] The world of the\NSelector Battles has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] All of the girls who\Nwere sealed into cards as LRIGs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,were able to return\Nto their former selves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,and their former lives,\Njust like I had hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,The Selector Battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I wonder if\Nthose girls even remember
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,what the game was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A game that was born from the\Nhatred and sorrow of one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone who never\Nknew love, only loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a game of broken rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,One where sadness awaited you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter what\Nselection you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,A lucky few of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,we were able to find\Nsomething within that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We found a way\Naround the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,a way to make our own selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The funny thing is, if we\Ndidn't participate in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,we never would have found out\Nwhat was really important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's not\Nthe end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead, it's a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So even if there's\Na long road ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,it's the one I've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I know there's\Na choice out there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,that sacrifices nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And I know I'm\Ngoing to find it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,So I keep looking.\NAnd that is my selection.
